PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776690659
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer to update House of
OL,4,CCommons on latest Mandelson revelations
OL,6,FFormer foreign secretary Sir James
OL,7,FCleverly told The Independent it is
OL,8,F"inconceivable" that the Prime
OL,9,FMinister and David Lammy were unaware
OL,10,Fof Lord Mandelson's failed security
OL,11,Fvetting.
OL,13,FLord Mandelson, a political
OL,14,Fappointment rather than a career
OL,15,Fdiplomat, was sacked from his
OL,16,FWashington role last September when
OL,17,Fmore details emerged about his
OL,18,Frelationship with paedophile financier
OL,19,FJeffrey Epstein, who died in 2019.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
