CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776690659
OL,3,CSir Keir Starmer to update House of
OL,4,CCommons on latest Mandelson revelations
OL,6,FSir Keir was already under fire over
OL,7,Fthe decision to give Lord Mandelson
OL,8,Fthe job, despite it being known that
OL,9,Fhis dealings with Epstein continued
OL,10,Fafter the financier's conviction for
OL,11,Fchild sex offences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
